      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="I don&#39;t receive the verification e-mail when registering to pixiv" class="article-title">
          I don&#39;t receive the verification e-mail when registering to pixiv
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>The verification e-mail will be sent from email address [no-reply@pixiv.net].<br>Be sure to add the above e-mail address to your e-mail account’s list of safe senders.</p>
<p>Also double check to make sure that the e-mail address is entered correctly.</p>
<p>In addition, your junk e-mail/spam filter settings may cause the e-mail to be blocked, or send the e-mail to your junk e-mail/spam folder.</p>
<p>If you do not receive the verification e-mail after a period of time, check the following:</p>
<p><strong>▪ If the e-mail is not delivered to your phone’s e-mail address</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Are domain specific access control and address specific access control set?</li>
<li>Do you use your cellphone service provider’s junk mail blocker service?</li>
<li>Is the transmission of e-mail delayed because of reception problems?</li>
</ul>
<p>* To verify the relevant settings operations, refer the manual that came with your phone, or contact the cell phone company.</p>
<p><strong>If the e-mail is not delivered to your PC’s address</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Is there a transmission delay on the sender-side e-mail service provider?</li>
<li>Was the e-mail sorted into the junk e-mail/spam folder?</li>
<li>Has the sender’s e-mail server exceeded its capacity?</li>
<li>Is the sender’s e-mail server experiencing technical difficulties?</li>
<li>Has the sender’s e-mail service provider detected the message to be junk e-mail/spam and deleted the message?</li>
<li>Is the transmission of e-mail delayed because of reception problems?</li>
</ul>
<p>* For information and the operation for changing settings, contact the PC manufacturer or provider.</p>
<p><strong>You can resend a verification email from the following page.</strong><br><a href="https://www.pixiv.net/setting_user.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.pixiv.net/setting_user.php</a></p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

